abstract: AUGUSTINE GROIIAN, the best soubrette on the French stage, is, at the age of 26, losing her eyesight. I write this paragraph with unmingled grief. The physicians have no hope-the shadow is settling over her, and in six months she will be irremediably blind. S She has retired to small country seat in the neighborhood of Paris, where she continues to receive the literary notabilities of the city.

abstract: Russia is almost devoid of an urban population. abstract: Quite a fluttering was occasioned in the Senate this afternoon, after Mr. DOUGLAS' amendment had been adopted, by an amendment offered by Mr. CHASE. The DOUGLAS amendment, it will be remembered, declares that it is not the intention of the bill to legislate Slavery into the Territories or to prohibit it therefrom, but to leave this and all other domestic questions to the decision of the people of the Territories, subject only to the Constitution.

abstract: THE SNOW, AND HOW THEY GET THROUGH IT.--The passage of the streets yesterday was a feat to be accomplished through desperate effort, fixed determination, and hope. The ridges of ice, interspersed in agreeable variety by small ponds of water and miniature ravines, wherein sleighs stuck fast, and wheeled vehicles became nonentities, made an amusing, albeit, a disagreeable panorama.

abstract: WALLACK'S THEATRE--Reproduction appears to be the order of the day here. " "Erastins," dished up from the French, and "Temptation," dished up from nothing in particular, have been given to good houses. The first work possesses a certain amount of ingenuity, and affords ample opportunity for good acting, Mrs. STEPHENS, Mr. LESTER and Mr. DYOTT do all that can be done for it, and certainly make enough of it. But "Temptation" is another affair altogether.

abstract: To the Editor of the New-York Daily Times: The advance in prices which has been going on for two or three years, is having pretty important bearings upon society. The main canse of this advance is supposed to be the immense gold discoveries in California and Australia. A short crop in Europe, and the prospect of a general war there, are no doubt operating just now upon the prices of breadstuffs and provisions.
